# Yma Presentation Template

This is a web presentation built with React + Vite + framer-motion.

Before making any changes, read these files:
0. `README.md` - main file with documentation.
1. `docs/AGENT.md` — project structure, slide anatomy, animation system, CSS classes
2. `docs/DESIGN.md` — branding, colors, fonts, spacing, do's and don'ts

Key rules:
- Wrap every visible element in `<A>` for scroll-triggered animations
- try not to generate SVG animations in code — use `<A>` variants, CSS `@keyframes`, or framer-motion hooks
- Use design tokens from `styles.css` — never hardcode colors or fonts
- After adding/removing slides, update `SLIDE_COUNT` in `App.jsx`

Template repo: https://github.com/Yma-Health/presentation_template.git

**CRITICAL — git safety:**
NEVER push to `presentation_template` repo. Before any git push, check `git remote -v`.
If origin points to `presentation_template` — create a NEW repo instead (see README for details).
